name: Introduction to Photography
details: Learn the basics of photography, including camera settings, composition, and exposure. Suitable for beginners.

name: Portrait Photography
details: Master the art of capturing stunning portraits, including lighting techniques and posing guidance.

name: Landscape Photography
details: Explore the beauty of landscapes and learn techniques to capture breathtaking scenic photographs.

name: Street Photography
details: Capture the essence of everyday life on the streets, documenting moments and telling stories through your photographs.

name: Product Photography
details: Learn the techniques for capturing high-quality product images for e-commerce, advertising, and catalogs.

name: Wildlife Photography
details: Discover the skills and patience required to photograph wildlife in their natural habitats, capturing stunning moments.

name: Night Photography
details: Learn to capture stunning photographs in low-light and night-time conditions, mastering exposure and creative techniques.

name: Fashion Photography
details: Learn the art of capturing fashion images, including working with models, posing, and creating captivating compositions.

name: Black and White Photography
details: Explore the artistry of black and white photography, learning techniques for capturing timeless monochromatic images.

name: Travel Photography
details: Capture the essence of your travel adventures, learning to tell stories through your photographs and document new cultures.

name: Food Photography
details: Master the art of food photography, including lighting, composition, and styling techniques to create appetizing images.

name: Mobile Photography
details: Learn to capture stunning photographs using your mobile phone, mastering composition, editing, and creative apps.
